comments: Schroder (OKC) maintains legal position as he moves alongside of Walker (BOS) during his drive.
Adams (OKC) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Adams (OKC) is late to the spot and makes contact to Tatum's (BOS) front which affects his driving shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) establishes legal position in Tatum's (BOS) path during the pick and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Theis (BOS) makes incidental contact to Paul's (OKC) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Paul (OKC) briefly grasps Hayward (BOS) during the pick and separate.
Schroder (OKC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Tatum (BOS) during his drive.
Theis (BOS) makes contact with Paul's (OKC) body during his drive that affects his SQBR.
Tatum (BOS) slightly extends his arm against Paul's (OKC) chest during his drive but contact does not affect his ability to defend through the play.
Paul (OKC) is not in a legal guarding position in the RA when he makes contact with Brown (BOS) on his driving shot.
Ferguson (OKC) establishes legal position in Theis (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Paul (OKC) reaches across Tatum's (BOS) body during his drive and dislodges the ball.
Adams (OKC) establishes legal position in Tatum's (BOS) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Theis (BOS) places his collapsing arm to Schroder's (OKC) side during his drive and removes it at the start of his upward shooting motion.
Paul (OKC) commits a take foul on Walker (BOS).
Smart (BOS) places his hand to Paul's (OKC) front but the contact is marginal and he continues his path to the basket.
Smart (BOS) creates contact with Ferguson (OKC) as he lifts his arms upward that subsequently creates contact with his head.
Schroder (OKC) makes contact with Hayward's (BOS) wrist during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) maintains legal position and cleanly deflects the ball away from Gilgous-Alexander (OKC).
Schroder (OKC) commits a take foul on Walker (BOS).
Brown (BOS) engages with Adams' (OKC) and disengages as he secures the loose ball.
Brown (BOS) makes marginal contact with Schroder (OKC) and disengages off ball.
